text:
:_ちょうちょ: 2:08:36, the exact moment of Victory, later of 8 months fighting between Cheaters which made her cry and Calculing mistakes, between another issues.

🎊🎉 Finally she obtained the 1st Place's Crown 👑

Never expected that epic moment... All started with 2020 August 15th, with that "Neeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee" which made her too recognizable. (That moment when server was busy)

:_るんるん: Now Rushia deserved this Victory... But some viewers will miss that "Neeeeee"... For someones who are caring of her, it was a crucial moment due to something explained by herself at between late October 2020 and early November 2020.
